  "title": "Accounts Executive (1-year contract)",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description</u></p><p>·      Perform AR/AP Functions</p><p>·      Preparation of monthly bank and AR/AP reconciliations</p><p>·      Fixed Asset Management</p><p>·      Donation Management</p><p>·      Assist in Audit Duties</p><p>·      Quarterly GST Submissions</p><p>·      Other Admin / Accounting duties as assigned</p><p><u>Requirements</u></p><p>·      Diploma or Degree in Accounting or relevant qualifications</p><p>·      At least 1-3 years of relevant experience preferred</p><p>·      Good command of MS Office applications</p><p>·      Experience with ERP systems preferred</p><p>·      Able to work independently as well as part of a team</p><p>·      Able to work under pressure and meet predetermined deadlines</p><p>·      Possess good interpersonal and communication skills, both written and verbal</p><p>·      Possess good organizational and analytical skills</p><ul><li>Familiarity with Office365 and Netsuite Oraclewould be an advantage</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
